                <h2>Odoo apps</h2>
                <p>The following apps were installed on your Odoo database and pre-configured as part of the Toy Store module. Take some time to discover them to take advantage of all the features that could be helpful for your store.</p>
                <div data-oe-protected="true" class="o_editor_banner o_not_editable lh-1 d-flex align-items-center alert alert-info pb-0 pt-3">
                <i class="o_editor_banner_icon mb-3 fst-normal">💡</i>
                <div data-oe-protected="false" class="w-100 px-3">
                        <p>Odoo apps share all the data in real time, so&nbsp;you won't have to encode customers' details or products multiple times.</p>
                </div>
                </div>
                <p><br /></p>
                <h3><img class="img img-fluid o_we_custom_image" src="/web/image/toy_store.ir_attachment_1056" /><span style="width: 40px;" class="oe-tabs"> </span>​Point of Sale</h3>
                <p>Manage customer purchases, returns, and exchanges. Access real-time sales data and inventory updates. Enhance customer satisfaction through loyalty programs and personalized offers.</p>
                <div data-oe-protected="true" class="o_editor_banner o_not_editable lh-1 d-flex align-items-center alert alert-info pb-0 pt-3">
                <i class="o_editor_banner_icon mb-3 fst-normal">💡</i>
                <div data-oe-protected="false" class="w-100 px-3">
                        <p>Point of Sale works on any device with a web browser, even if you are temporarily offline.</p>
                </div>
                </div>
                <p>
                <a class="btn btn-secondary mb-2" href="https://www.odoo.com/slides/point-of-sale-28">🎓 Tutorials</a>&nbsp;
                <a class="btn btn-secondary mb-2" href="https://www.odoo.com/documentation/latest/applications/sales/point_of_sale.html">📖 Documentation</a>
                </p>
                <div class="o_editor_banner o_not_editable lh-1 d-flex align-items-center alert alert-success pb-0 pt-3" data-oe-protected="true">
                <i class="o_editor_banner_icon mb-3 fst-normal">🚀</i>
                <div class="w-100 px-3" data-oe-protected="false">
                        <h4>Demo:&nbsp; complete a cash sale and issue an invoice to your customer</h4>
                        <ul>
                        <li>In Point of Sale, open the <em>Shop</em> register.</li>
                        <li>Select a customer or create a new one, and add products.</li>
                        <li>Click on <em>Payment</em>, then select <em>Cash</em>&nbsp;as payment method and&nbsp;<em>Invoice</em>&nbsp;next to the total amount.</li>
                        <li>Finalize the checkout, then open the PDF file with the invoice.</li>
                        </ul>
                </div>
                </div>
                <p><br /></p>
                <h3><img class="img img-fluid o_we_custom_image" src="/web/image/toy_store.ir_attachment_1058" /><span style="width: 40px;" class="oe-tabs"> </span>​Website and eCommerce</h3>
                <p>Create a professional website, design beautiful product pages, and process online orders seamlessly. Drive sales through marketing and SEO optimization.</p>
                <p>
                <a class="btn btn-secondary" href="https://www.odoo.com/slides/website-25">🎓 Website tutorials</a>&nbsp;
                <a class="btn btn-secondary" href="https://www.odoo.com/documentation/latest/applications/websites/website.html">📖 Website documentation</a>
                </p>
                <p>
                <a href="https://www.odoo.com/slides/ecommerce-26" class="btn btn-secondary">🎓 eCommerce tutorials</a>&nbsp;
                <strong><a href="https://www.odoo.com/documentation/latest/applications/websites/ecommerce.html" class="btn btn-secondary">📖 eCommerce documentation</a></strong>
                </p>
                <div data-oe-protected="true" class="o_editor_banner o_not_editable lh-1 d-flex align-items-center alert alert-success pb-0 pt-3">
                <i class="o_editor_banner_icon mb-3 fst-normal">🚀</i>
                <div data-oe-protected="false" class="w-100 px-3">
                        <h4>Demo: order online with the <em>Demo</em> payment method</h4>
                        <p>The <em>Demo</em>&nbsp;payment method&nbsp;is for testing purposes. It is safe to play with, and you can choose whether&nbsp;the payment is successful or not.</p>
                        <ul>
                        <li>Go to Website and add products to your cart.</li>
                        <li>Go to checkout and use <em>Demo</em>&nbsp;as the payment method, with the <em>Payment Status</em>&nbsp;set as <em>Successful</em>.​<br /></li>
                        </ul>
                </div>
                </div>
                <p><br /></p>
                <h3><img class="img img-fluid o_we_custom_image" src="/web/image/toy_store.ir_attachment_1062" /><span style="width: 40px;" class="oe-tabs"> </span>​Invoicing</h3>
                <p>Issue professional-looking invoices in no time,&nbsp;configure the fiscal settings such as the tax rates according to your country's needs, and set up online payment methods.</p>
                <p>
                <a href="https://www.odoo.com/slides/accounting-and-invoicing-19" class="btn btn-secondary mb-2">🎓 Tutorials</a>&nbsp;
                <a href="https://www.odoo.com/documentation/latest/applications/finance/accounting.html" class="btn btn-secondary mb-2">📖 Documentation</a>
                </p>
                <p><br /></p>
                <h3><img class="img img-fluid o_we_custom_image" src="/web/image/toy_store.ir_attachment_1059" /><span style="width: 40px;" class="oe-tabs"> </span>​Purchase</h3>
                <p>Create and manage purchase orders, track vendor performance, and ensure timely deliveries. Optimize purchasing decisions based on product demand and supplier performance.<br /></p>
                <p>
                <a class="btn btn-secondary mb-2" href="https://www.odoo.com/slides/purchase-23">🎓 Tutorials</a>&nbsp;
                <a class="btn btn-secondary mb-2" href="https://www.odoo.com/documentation/latest/applications/inventory_and_mrp/purchase.html">📖 Documentation</a>
                </p>
                <p><br /></p>
                <h3><img class="img img-fluid o_we_custom_image" src="/web/image/toy_store.ir_attachment_1060" /><span style="width: 40px;" class="oe-tabs"> </span>​Inventory</h3>
                <p>Accurately track product quantities and locations. Prepare products for shipment, including packing and labeling. Use automated reordering rules to prevent stockouts and overstocking.</p>
                <p>
                <a class="btn btn-secondary mb-2" href="https://www.odoo.com/slides/inventory-24">🎓 Tutorials</a>&nbsp;
                <a class="btn btn-secondary mb-2" href="https://www.odoo.com/documentation/latest/applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory.html">📖 Documentation</a>
                </p>
                <p><br /></p>
